data.description: This beautiful ranch-style home provides the perfect space for comfortable living with 3 beds, 2 baths, & a 1 car garage. Featuring a completely upgraded kitchen, porcelain & hardwood floors throughout, & charming curb appeal. The highlight of this home is the remodeled Florida room, offering a light-filled retreat, perfect for a home office, or play area. Step outside into the backyard & you'll be greeted by a variety of fruit trees, adding a touch of nature that provides the perfect setting for outdoor relaxation & entertainment. Located in the desirable city of Sunrise, FL, this home is not only aesthetically pleasing but also offers a prime location. Whether you're looking for nearby amenities, great schools, or easy access to major highways, this property has it all.
